title: Truecaller-Pro-8.47 (mrkiven0)
description:
Truecaller Premium
Truecaller identifies unknown callers and blocks nuisance calls. See names and photos of people who call, even if they aren’t saved in your phonebook. And know when friends are free to talk, making your calling experience smarter and more delightful. With a community-based spam list of over 200 million users, Truecaller is the only phone app you’ll ever need.
Features
>Always see who’s calling — works for saved contacts and unknown numbers
>Block PPI nuisance callers and telemarketers
>Search for any name or number
>Make calls directly from the app
>No more unknown numbers in your call history
>See when your friends are free to talk
>Copy a number anywhere (e.g. website or apps) and Truecaller will tell you who it belongs to
WHATS CRACKED
>Premium features Unlocked
WHAT’S NEW
Improved battery and memory consumption
Various bug fixes and improvements
Spam Folder – keep all your junk spam SMS away from your Inbox
Many new themes including Pitch Black
Truecaller PRO is now a recurring subscription – no need to pay every month
How to Install ?
>Download & Install the Apk from the links given below
>Done ! Enjoy
